  <summary date="2023-08-20T22:23:41Z" status="Introduced in House">PFAS Reference Standards Act

This bill requires the Environmental Protection Agency to require manufacturers of perfluoroalkyl or polyfluoroalkyl substances, commonly referred to as PFAS, to submit an analytical reference standard for each PFAS it has manufactured since ten years prior to the enactment of this bill.</summary>
